HEADWORD: Archimagus
<hw>Ar`chi*ma"gus</hw> <pr>(⟦aum⟧r`k⟦icr⟧m⟦amac⟧"g⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.; pref. <ets>archi-</ets> + L.
<ets>magus</ets>, Gr. <grk>ma`gos</grk>, a Magian.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The high priest of the Persian Magi, or worshipers of
